",["$r","p",null,{"children":["If none of this worked, please comment in ",["$r","a",null,{"href":"https://github.com/facebook/react/issues/13991","target":"_blank","rel":"nofollow noopener noreferrer","children":"this issue"}]," and we’ll try to help. Try to create a small reproducing example — you might discover the problem as you’re doing it."]}]]}]]
